  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Providing Safe Drinking Water for  War Affected.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project is all about providing safe drinking water to 100 underserved families in a war affected remote village and the villagers have been suffering due to lack of water for nearly 60 years. To cure this critical situation, we hope to  construct 02 water storage tanks with the capacity of each 60,000 Ltrs , 02 water wells and  02 pump houses.   The main beneficiaries of this project are children,youth,infants and women. main objective is to provide safe drinking water.</narrative>
  </description>
